<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "home", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
  </head>
  <body>
<!--Background Video-->
    <div class="card bg-dark text-white" id='video_container'>
     <!--Background Video <%= video_tag( 'iceland.mp4', autoplay: true, loop: true, muted: true, id:'video')%>-->
     <%= image_tag 'home/image_1.jpeg'%>
      <div class="card-img-overlay">
      <!--Title, Buttons & Content-->
          <div class='row'>
            <div class='col-6'>
              <h2 class='home_title_layout' id='home_title'>NEVER STOP EXPLORING<h2>
              <h2 class='home_title_layout'>DISCOVER THE LAND OF FIRE & ICE<h2>
            </div>
          </div>  
          <div class='row'>
            <div class='col-5'>
              <p class='home_content' id='home_hidden'>
                Adventurers are drawn to Iceland because of its stunning natural beauty. The landscape is nothing short of mystical. The scenary promises an endless series of snow-covered volcanoes, mountains, waterfalls, canyons and ice fields. With a rugged, “other-worldly” terrain, the Nordic icy views are like nothing you'll see in the rest of the world.
              </p>
              <p class='home_content'>
                Use our interactive <%= link_to "Map", "/map", id:'home_map_link'%> to guide you to some of Iceland's picteresque sights & see what our users thought about these magnificent natural wonders. Sign up and join our community to gain the ability to post comments & your images with our community. 
              </p>
              <!--Render Links-->
            <%= render 'user/session_manager_home' %>
            </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>